  "text": "Accordingly, class Reder is endowed with method find(String spec), which takes a list of static resources as the input parameter spec; transforms it into the equivalent Classified Advertisement (ClassAd) 1 [CITATION_1] ; invokes the appropriate RB service; and finally returns a list of available hosts satisfying the request. Figure 2(a) shows the interactions between Reder and the RB via the CoG library. Results from RB are appropriately cached into Reder to avoid frequent and time consuming queries.",
